{
  "chapter": 73,
  "chapter_summary": "第七十三回\"买影人\"。芮玮来到少华山慈悲庵，欲闯关见野儿。第一关由茶棚老妪把守，需抱起玄铁木茶桶倒满三碗茶，再以三种不同方式饮尽。芮玮以内力轻松过关。第二关须攀上三十二丈峭壁，芮玮以飞龙八步连踩八步登顶。平台上三名慈悲庵小尼姑以先天掌迎敌，芮玮二招即败，心灰意冷跳崖而下，被老妪接住。下山途中遇太华山老人，老人指点他去找\"买影人\"——太华山一位老比丘可引见能看穿所有掌法破绽的高手，学会破解先天掌之法。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lao_yu",
      "text": "敢问老婆婆慈悲庵在上面吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lao_yu",
      "text": "闯关！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "老妪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "喝茶吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lao_yu",
      "text": "晚辈口不渴，谢谢啦！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "老妪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "既知闯关，不知喝茶上山是第一关吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "老妪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "三碗倒满，不准溅出茶来。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lao_yu",
      "text": "可以吧？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "老妪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "喝啊！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "老妪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "三碗茶三种喝法，喝完过关，可记着，滴出一点前功尽弃，那时请回。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "老妪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好功夫！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "老妪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "请用最后一碗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lao_yu",
      "text": "第三碗有点献丑了，请不要见笑。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "老妪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "别得意，还有两关，请上吧。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lao_yu",
      "text": "得罪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老婆婆再见。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "老妪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "看你能上拔多高。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "老妪",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "第一关过！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_que_ban_ni_gu",
      "speaker_name": "雀斑尼姑",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "施主请闯第二关。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_que_ban_ni_gu",
      "text": "第二关在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_que_ban_ni_gu",
      "speaker_name": "雀斑尼姑",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不知道吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zui_xiao_ni_gu",
      "speaker_name": "最小尼姑",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你不知道规矩闯什么关，告诉你，第二关便是我师姐妹三人守，随便哪个，你胜了便过关。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_zui_xiao_ni_gu",
      "text": "不行，不行，小妹妹，叫你们大人出来。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zui_xiao_ni_gu",
      "speaker_name": "最小尼姑",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "谁是你小妹妹！来！来！我看你根本不是我两位师姐的对手，跟我比比还能撑持一会。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zui_xiao_ni_gu",
      "speaker_name": "最小尼姑",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "请呀！你不打请回。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zui_xiao_ni_gu",
      "speaker_name": "最小尼姑",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你倒乖巧，知道我要打你耳光。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_que_ban_ni_gu",
      "speaker_name": "雀斑尼姑",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "施主不要难过，请回吧。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_que_ban_ni_gu",
      "speaker_name": "雀斑尼姑",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "施主能闯过第一关，武功远在我师姊妹之上，你败的原因……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wei_shuo_hua_ni_gu",
      "speaker_name": "未说话的尼姑",
      "listener": "char_que_ban_ni_gu",
      "text": "师姐你怎么啦？跟他多说什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zui_xiao_ni_gu",
      "speaker_name": "最小尼姑",
      "listener": "char_que_ban_ni_gu",
      "text": "师姐，你对她关什么心……",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "老妪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "要自杀别在这里自杀，想害我老太婆是不是？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lao_yu",
      "text": "多谢老婆婆救命之恩。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "老妪",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "去吧，去吧，能破先天掌再来闯关。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "老弟，老弟！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "怎么，闯关没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "闯是闯了，可惜晚辈太差劲了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "可惜，可惜。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "一点也不可惜，晚辈实在无法敌那先天掌。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "以你内家修为，别说三关，十关，二十关也能闯。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "功力徒高，破不了人家的掌招有得何用！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "先前我记得跟你说过，不要气馁，那时我就想你可能闯不过先天掌，其实武学中掌招只是一种魔术，真正的武功，还是看谁的内家功夫高。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "魔术一学就会，内家功夫却是硬碰硬的，我本以为你内功高，掌法一定不差，哪知掌法太差，怎么二招就败了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "晚辈实在无能，这生永不谈武了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "叫你不要气馁，大丈夫逢难弥坚，气馁什么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "请老丈再指一条明路。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你是不是决心要见那位野儿的尼姑？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "决心要见。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好，你既有这番决心，我就告诉你去找一个人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "找谁呀？他能帮我解决问题吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你的问题，在能不能破先天掌，先天掌一破，我保你第三关能过，那时不就见到野儿了吗？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "谁能破先天掌？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "掌法高低等于谁的魔术灵不灵，但天下魔术皆有破绽，一个魔术大师，他能看穿所有魔术的漏洞，同样的道理，一个精于掌法者能够看穿所有掌法的破绽。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "天下有能看穿所有掌法破绽的人吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "有，你只要告诉他先天掌这名字，他能在短时间内教你这掌法的破招。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "此人何处？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你记不记得，太华山那座小得可怜的尼庵，和里面住的又老又丑的比丘尼？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "难道她能破天下各种掌法？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "老人",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不，而是她能带你见想见的掌法高手，你只要到该处，见到老比丘，说我要见买影人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lao_ren",
      "text": "买影人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 73,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    }
  ],
